At Brightblue Apps, we are very careful about your and your children’s privacy. We know how important this is.
In our app “Turtle Math for Kids – Children Learn Numbers and Addition”:
We do not collect any personal information about the users.
We do not collect information such as first name, last name, address, phone number or e-mail address.
We do not collect data about your location.
We do not have any social networks integrated in our app.
We do not have advertising banners in our app.
The app may contain In-App Purchases, but they can be made only after the built-in parental control.
If you have any questions or concerns, please
Contact us
